.paywall__text
  p.paywall__intro.
    We’re sorry to say that, but your account will be inactive until you set up
    payment.

  div(ng-show="planRecommendationReasonHtml" ng-bind-html="planRecommendationReasonHtml")

  p.
    If you’ve tried Contentful and liked it, please set up your
    preferred payment method and continue managing content.

  button.advice__action.cfnext-btn-primary-action.modal-dialog__controls-confirm(
    ng-click="dialog.confirm(model); setUpPayment()"
    type="button") Set up payment

  p.paywall__bottom-note
    | If you need to extend your trial, if this message caught you by surprise,
    | or you’re unsure why this has happened, please&#32;
    a(ng-click="openIntercom()" role="button") talk to us
    |  directly.

.paywall__recommended-subscription(ng-show="planHtml")
  h2 Recommended plan
  div(ng-bind-html="planHtml")
